ok. i made it:) - works<br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">   .ineschr 0</div><br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">Start:<br />   jsr tiles</div><br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">tiles:                  ;copy defchr tiles to VRAM<br /><br />        lda #0          ;set VRAM row for first row of tiles &#40;$0000&#41;<br />        sta $2006<br />        lda #$10        ;blank firs tile<br />        sta $2006<br />        ldy #0<br />tiles1:<br />        lda tileset,y<br />        sta $2007<br />        iny<br />        cpy #$20        ;number of tiles x 16 bytes &#40;$10&#41; per tile<br />        bne tiles1<br />        rts</div><br /><br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">tileset:<br /><br />   .defchr $23333331,\<br />      $32000013,\<br />      $30200103,\<br />      $30021003,\<br />      $30012003,\<br />      $30100203,\<br />      $31000023,\<br />      $13333332<br /><br />   .defchr $30000003,\<br />      $00000000,\<br />      $00223300,\<br />      $00211300,\<br />      $00211300,\<br />      $00223300,\<br />      $00000000,\<br />      $30000003</div><br /><br />Now i want animate moving tile, somebody know how to easy make it??<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=411">sdm</a> — Mon Jul 30, 2007 9:00 am</p><hr />
